- Generic mass-marketing language or templated promos unrelated to an existing conversation
- Bulk marketing traits (e.g., marketing platform footer/unsubscribe) combined with no clear prior relationship or consent
- Irrelevant vendor solicitations not tied to ongoing work or context

Do NOT mark as spam when the content appears to be:
- Replies/forwards, ongoing threads, calendar invites, personal messages
