- Opt-in newsletters from recognized brands the user plausibly subscribed to (unless deceptive or clearly irrelevant)

Evidence to consider (lightweight, not prescriptive):
- Content intent (promotional vs conversational/transactional)
- Threading cues: "Re:", "Fwd:", quoted content, In-Reply-To/References headers
